 SHOWPATTERN x sizex y sizey pat_type

 draws a pattern on screen, at location 'x y' (in spectral coordinate)
     and of sizex , sizey  (in spectral coordinate)
 The pattern can be chosen with pat_type :
             x  cross
             +  cross
             *  star
             s  square
             d  diamond
             c  circle
             b  box ( + and square )
Color is SCOLOR

see also : SHOWLINE SCOLOR point_cross
